      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i noticed something weird with my smart thermostat and the smart fridge. every time i get really stressed or start crying, the thermostat drops like 3 degrees almost instantly, and then the fridge compressor starts running way more than usual. like it's almost simultaneous. is there some kind of sensor sync happening between them that i didnt set up? it feels weirdly timed.",
